/**
 * Built-in Skill Pack Metadata
 *
 * The actual skill content lives in src/runtime/skills/packs/{domain}/{skill}/SKILL.md
 * — these are the real Anthropic & Partners plugin skills copied from Claude Code's
 * marketplace. They are loaded by skill.ts at runtime via filesystem scan.
 *
 * This file only exports the pack registry metadata: which npm package ID maps to
 * which set of skill slash commands. This is used by the Plugin Marketplace UI.
 */

